The '''Colonists''' were one of the two social factions of the [[Outbound Flight Colony]], the others being the [[Survivors (Outbound Flight)|Survivors]]. The Colonists were the ones who had been born after the ''[[Outbound Flight]]'' crashed in [[The Redoubt/Legends|the Redoubt]].

The [[Charter]] guaranteed that both factions were represented in the [[Managing Council]].

